WEBVTT

NOTE Captions describe each visible step of the silent profanity-filter demo.

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
The Profanity Filter playground loads in dark mode with a live SignalR connection.

2
00:00:01.500 --> 00:00:05.500
A user types a sentence containing profanity. The right-hand panel rewrites it live as they type.

3
00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:07.200
Default Asterisk strategy: each profane word becomes asterisks.

4
00:00:07.300 --> 00:00:09.700
Strategy switched to Emoji: a random emoji replaces each profane word.

5
00:00:09.800 --> 00:00:12.200
Strategy switched to Redacted Rectangle: a black bar covers each word.

6
00:00:12.300 --> 00:00:14.700
Strategy switched to Middle Swear Emoji: the first and last letters stay, the middle becomes a swearing-face emoji.

7
00:00:14.800 --> 00:00:17.100
Strategy switched to Bleep: each word is replaced by the literal text bleep.

8
00:00:17.200 --> 00:00:19.700
Strategy switched to First Letter Then Asterisk: the first letter remains, the rest become asterisks.

9
00:00:19.800 --> 00:00:21.500
Strategy badge and match chips at the bottom update live with every change.
